steps.html_instructions:
Head northwest on Steve Flanders Square toward Broadway/Canyon of Heroes
Restricted usage road
Steve Flanders Square turns slightly left and becomes Murray Street
Turn right onto Church St
Slight left onto 6th Ave/Avenue of the Americas
Turn left onto Watts St

Continue onto I-78 W/Clifford Milburn Holland Tunnel/Holland Tunnel
Continue to follow I-78 W
Entering New Jersey
Keep left at the fork to continue on NJ-139 W
Take the US-1 Truck/US-9 Truck exit toward I-280/Jersey City/Kearny
Continue onto Charlotte Ave
Keep right to continue toward Newark-Jersey City Turnpike
Continue onto Newark-Jersey City Turnpike
Take the Interstate 280 W ramp
Merge onto I-280 W

Continue onto I-80 W
Partial toll road
Entering Pennsylvania

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-80 W
Entering Ohio
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-80 W, follow signs for Cleveland

Take the I-80 W exit
Toll road

Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-80 W/Cleveland and merge onto I-80 W
Partial toll road
Entering Indiana

Continue onto I-90 W
Partial toll road
Entering Illinois
Take exit 51H for I-290 W toward W Elsenhower Expy/W Suburbs
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for Congress Parkway/Chicago Loop and merge onto I-290 E
Continue straight onto W Congress Pkwy
Turn left onto S Dearborn St
Take the 1st left onto W Van Buren St
Take the 1st right onto S Federal St
